-- Luxottica to Consider Acquisitions Again From 2011, Chief Tells Il Sole
-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 2010-10-26T05:42:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/luxottica-to-consider-acquisitions-again-from-2011-ceo-tells-il-sole.html
Luxottica Group SpA  may start
looking at acquisitions again in 2011, Chief Executive Officer
Andrea Guerra said in an interview with daily Il Sole 24 Ore.  Luxottica will consider more "significant" acquisitions
throughout the world starting next year, Guerra told Sole.  To contact the reporter on this story:
